{"tid":593916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮檢基：姚松炎敗選因初選分化支持者","createTime":"2018-03-15T11:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T11:45:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"102bd2249eed52016cee95c2a400ee4ccb44453d","tid":593916,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】姚松炎在九龍西立法會補選落敗，外界質疑民協無全力助選。馮檢基接受訪問時指，姚松炎在泛民初選分化支持者，令他難以拉攏民協選民支持。又強調民協幫忙做了不少宣傳工作，否認放軟手腳。<br />\n<br />\n在泛民初選落敗的馮檢基，被質疑在補選中未有全力幫姚松炎拉票，令他在民協票倉流失支持。馮檢基接受本台訪問時指，敗選只能歸咎初選分化了民主派支持者，他強調民協成員並無放軟手腳。<br />\n<br />\n但在選舉日馮檢基無為姚松炎站台，並在傍晚前往台灣公幹。他指，姚松炎參選議題太單一，只著重DQ事件，關顧基層的政綱不足都令他流失選票。<br />\n<br />\n九龍西選區尚有一個立法會議席，因為劉小麗宣誓無效而出缺。馮檢基表示，如果劉小麗參選他不會出來爭。至於會否有劉小麗的後備人選，馮檢基稱言之尚早，當務之急是檢討泛民初選機制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=257484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D257484&d=tlv2LMwuHyvCW5WbeHa9MvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=65813885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D257484&h=453eec62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=257484</a>"},{"pid":"cb3988b028336e04e15450162655cabb4c7800d5","tid":593916,"uid":72306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:38:02.000Z","msg":"阿基係咁撚姚朱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d70555fa1cb428bdaa1e8d05ed45a6661d07e57","tid":593916,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老馮"},{"pid":"ead322ee59296c8dafa738cf883e30bb5dbc5559","tid":593916,"uid":18954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"咁姚政鋼又真係偏重左dq既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebda714603dbd5af5c3e301071129bbbaeb44662","tid":59391